# setup Scala By Scala files
https://spark.apache.org/downloads.html
 Follow the Below procedure
 1. after download check the spark download folder
 2. open command prompt => type ls -ltr
 3. by using cd command enter the bin folder. like cd Bin => /Users/pradeep/Desktop/spark-3.0.0-preview-bin-hadoop2.7/bin
 4. type ls command and check spark-shell
 5. ./spark-shell
(base) pradeeps-MacBook-Air:bin pradeep$ ./spark-shell
